name: StateCapitalsQuiz
0:
”Alexa open state capitals quiz.”
”Alexa launch state capitals quiz.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: state capitals quiz
des:
Have Alexa quiz you on the U.S. state capitals!

Alexa will say the name of a state, and you will need to respond with the name of the capital. If you do not know an answer, you can say, "I give up." At any time, you can say, "Stop," and Alexa will tell you how you did on the quiz. Otherwise, she will go through all 50 states. Can you get them all correct?

To launch, simply say, "Alexa, open State Capitals Quiz."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
